These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, tennis, lacrosse, cricket
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
2. the person drinking sprite is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | sprite   | iced-tea    | milk    | hot-chocolate |
| Sport      | cricket | weightlifting | lacrosse | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, soy-milk, almond-milk
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, cranberry, peach, cucumber
1. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
3. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
4. the person drinking lemonade is not the person eating cranberry##6
5. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating peach##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | lemonade  | soy-milk    | 7up | almond-milk    |
| Food       | cucumber | cranberry | peach  | cabbage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade, mirinda, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, firefighter, project-manager, paramedic
1. the person drinking cola is not the analyst##6
2. the firefighter is not the person drinking mirinda##6
3. the project-manager is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
4. the firefighter is the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the firefighter##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
7. the analyst is on the far left or far right##3
8. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the paramedic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | cola       | lemonade  | almond-milk  | mirinda |
| Job        | project-manager | paramedic | firefighter | analyst  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, goat, ferret, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, taxi, van
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
3. the person driving the van is not the owner of the goat##6
4. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
6. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | goat | ferret | horse     | turtle |
| Transport   | bus     | taxi    | bike | van    |

