.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, tea, lemonade
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, ship, roller, quad-bike
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
3. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
4. the person drinking cola is not the person driving the quad-bike##6
5. the person driving the subway is not the person drinking coffee##6
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | coffee        | lemonade | tea | cola |
| Transport   | quad-bike | subway | ship     | roller   |

