.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, musical, fantasy, epic
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, british, argentine, mexican
1. the indonesian is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is not the british##6
3. the indonesian is on the far right##1
4. the british is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
5. the person watching fantasy movies is the person watching fantasy movies##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the indonesian##5
7. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
8. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
9. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | fantasy    | scientific  | epic   |
| Nationality   | argentine  | mexican | british | indonesian |

