.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, family, animation, musical
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, metal, indie, r&b
1. the fan indie is on the left or right of the fan jazz##3
2. the fan indie is not the person watching family movies##6
3. the person watching adventure movies is the fan metal##1
4. the fan jazz is on the left or right of the fan r&b##3
5. the fan indie is on the far left##1
6. the person watching family movies is the fan jazz##1
7. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the fan jazz##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | family     | animation | adventure |
| Music-Genre   | indie | jazz | r&b      | metal         |

