4. the designer is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the designer##3
6. the pilot is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
7. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the firefighter##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | sprite        | almond-milk      | mirinda          |
| Job        | pilot | designer | firefighter | paramedic |

