.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, musician, electrician, entrepreneur
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, bike, boat, jet-ski
1. the engineer is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bike is not the entrepreneur##6
3. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the electrician##5
4. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is the electrician##1
7. the engineer is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
8. the musician is somewhere to the right of the entrepreneur##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | engineer  | electrician | entrepreneur    | musician |
| Transport   | bike | jet-ski | boat | snowmobile  |

