.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, lizard, horse, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, soccer, cycling, badminton
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is not the owner of the pony##6
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the owner of the horse is not the person who's sport is badminton##6
6. the person who's sport is soccer is not the owner of the lizard##6
7. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the horse is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | horse | pony        | goldfish  | lizard     |
| Sport   | biathlon     | badminton | soccer | cycling |

