.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, writing, gardening, magic-tricks
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, folk, blues, salsa
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
2. the fan folk is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##5
3. the fan blues is not the person who's hobby is gardening##6
4. the person who's hobby is writing is between the fan salsa and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the fan folk is between the fan trance and the person who's hobby is photography##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | gardening | writing    | photography | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | trance         | folk | salsa   | blues     |

