4. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
5. the person driving the tram is not the person eating lime##6
6. the person eating pomegranate is not the person driving the scooter##6
7. the person eating mango is somewhere to the left of the person eating pomegranate##5
8. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | pumpkin  | mango | pomegranate | lime |
| Transport   | tram | scooter     | jet-ski     | skateboard    |

