.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, kale, cherry, zucchini
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, spy, scientific, satire
1. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the right of the person eating kale##5
2. the person eating kale is not the person watching spy movies##6
3. the person eating nectarine is the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
5. the person eating nectarine is between the person eating kale and the person watching crime movies##2
6. the person eating kale is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
