2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the owner of the pony is not the person who's hobby is sudoku##6
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
8. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | card-games | gardening | sudoku | writing |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | frog      | rabbit  | pony       |

