.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, soy-milk, coffee
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, car, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
6. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | 7up | coffee      | soy-milk   |
| Transport   | scooter  | subway   | car | helicopter |

 